[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "欢迎来到谁让他炼器的！第一章，入宗考试。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨来到问道宗参加入宗考试。他的炼器理念是模块化设计、用户体验和底层逻辑闭环。简单来说，他的法宝不按常理出牌。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "问道宗，传说中最正统的修仙宗门。今天，我终于来了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你是来参加入宗考试的？报上名来。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨。特长是炼器。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "炼器？上一个说自己擅长炼器的，现在还在后山修丹炉。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我的炼器跟别人不太一样。我追求的是用户体验和底层逻辑闭环。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "说人话。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "就是我的法宝会自己思考。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "好，考试任务：炼制一件法器。限时一炷香。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你有什么材料？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我带了三百个微型隐藏机关、两个指纹识别阵法、和一个自动格式化模块。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "这不是炼器，这是在造兵器工厂吧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "老师您有所不知，模块化才是未来。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "模块化设计，指纹识别，自动格式化防偷，启动！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "自动寻路飞剑，完成！"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "这把剑怎么在抖？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "这是智能振动模式，帮助它定位目标。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "定位什么目标？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "灵气密度最高的目标。这是它的核心算法。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等，它为什么朝我飞过来？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "因为您的储物袋灵气浓度最高。它很聪明吧？"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "这是抢劫吧！这是抢劫吧？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不不不，这是自动寻路功能。攻击和抢劫只是副产物。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "把你的破剑收回去！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "收不回来了，我忘加停止按钮了。"
      }
    ]
  },
